'''麥克法蘭公司'''（[[英文|英文]]：'''McFarland & Company, Inc.'''）是一家總部位於[[美国|美国]][[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]][[傑斐遜_(北卡羅來納州)|傑斐遜]]的[[出版公司|出版公司]]，成立於1979年，主要出版[[学术期刊|学术期刊]]、[[專著|專著]]和[[參考書|參考書]]。<ref name="UNC">{{Cite web |url=http://www.unc.edu/depts/ppps/NCSLNews/houses/houses.html |title=The North Carolina Sports Literature Newsletter {{!}} Publishing Houses – What's New<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2013-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130319200828/http://www.unc.edu/depts/ppps/NCSLNews/houses/houses.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mountaintimes.com/mtweekly/2004/0930/mcfarland.php3 |title=The Mountain Times Online<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2012-09-03 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120903161005/http://archives.mountaintimes.com/mtweekly/2004/0930/mcfarland.php3 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mcfarlandpub.com/about.html |title=McFarland – Publisher of Reference and Scholarly Books<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2011-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110503182614/http://mcfarlandpub.com/about.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

根據美國週報《[[Mountain_Times|Mountain Times]]》在2007年的報道，麥克法蘭公司每年出版約275部學術專著和參考書<ref name="MT03312005">{{cite web|url=http://archives.mountaintimes.com/mtweekly/2005/0331/mcfarland.php3|title=McFarland & Company Announces Promotion|work=''[[Mountain_Times|Mountain Times]]''|date=2005-03-31|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215170314/http://archives.mountaintimes.com/mtweekly/2005/0331/mcfarland.php3|archivedate=2013-12-15}}</ref><ref name="MT12132007">{{Cite news |url=http://archives.mountaintimes.com/mtweekly/2007/1213/mcfarland.php3 |title=VP Celebrates 25 Years at McFarland |date=2007-12-13 |work=''[[Mountain_Times|Mountain Times]]'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215170426/http://archives.mountaintimes.com/mtweekly/2007/1213/mcfarland.php3 |archivedate=2013-12-15}}</ref>，2015年的相關報道則顯示該數量已達到約350部<ref name="guidebook">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UsyRBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA736|title=''2015 Writer's Market: The Most Trusted Guide to Getting Published''|last=Brewer|first=Robert Lee|date=2014-08-05|publisher={{le|Writer's Digest Books}} |location=[[辛辛那提|Cincinnati]] | isbn=978-1-59963-860-7}}</ref>。

==期刊列表==
麥克法蘭公司出版的[[学术期刊|学术期刊]]如下：
*《棒球：早期賽事期刊》（Base Ball: A Journal of the Early Game）– 主題為[[棒球|棒球]]的早期歷史，即棒球從起源之初到1920年間的相關賽事<ref name="journals">{{Cite web |url=http://www.mcfarlandbooks.com/customers/journals/ |title=Journals |work=''McFarlandBooks.com'' |publisher=McFarland & Company |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150420040701/http://www.mcfarlandbooks.com/customers/journals/|archivedate=2015-04-20}}</ref>
*《黑球：黑人聯盟期刊》（Black Ball: A Journal of the Negro Leagues）– 主題為黑人棒球，包括[[黑人聯盟|黑人大联盟和小联盟]]，以及黑人联盟形成之前的黑人棒球赛<ref name="journals"/>
*《線索：偵查期刊》（Clues: A Journal of Detection）– 主題為印刷品、電視及電影中的各類神秘故事和偵探故事<ref name="journals"/>
*《[[信息倫理學期刊|信息倫理學期刊]]》（Journal of Information Ethics）– 主題為[[信息伦理学|信息伦理学]]和[[信息科学|信息科学]]<ref name="guidebook"/>
*《領土與海事研究期刊》（Journal of Territorial and Maritime Studies）– 主題為全球领土与海事问题<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.journalofterritorialandmaritimestudies.net/about-us|title=JTMS Journal of Territorial and Maritime Studies|website=''JTMS Journal of Territorial and Maritime Studies''|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20180123221511/https://www.journalofterritorialandmaritimestudies.net/about-us|archivedate=2018-01-23}}</ref><ref name="journals"/>
*《[[北韓評論|-{A]]》（North Korean Review）– 主題為[[北韓|北韓]]的“複雜性及其對全球穩定的威脅”<ref name="journals"/>

